&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Finance and Compliance Assistant&lt;/strong&gt; – Kingskerswell &amp; Ipplepen Health Centre, Newton Abbot, Devon&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kingskerswell &amp; Ipplepen Health centre are seeking to recruit a Finance and Compliance Assistant to support the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kingskerswell &amp; Ipplepen is a successful and well regarded GP training and dispensing medical practice in South Devon. We have been rated outstanding by CQC in all five key areas and rank amongst the highest nationally in our patient survey results. The practice has an excellent reputation for clinical outcomes and delivering quality patient centred services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hourly rate is £10.10 and we are ideally looking to recruit for 37.5 hours a week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;T&amp;Cs – 5 weeks annual leave + Pro rata share of bank holidays and competitive pay. See supporting document on benefits of employment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The practice team is a friendly dynamic workforce of professional Clinical staff and excellent Admin support, with a proactive staff wellbeing ethos. The practice uses TPPP SystmOne clinical system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;To apply please send your CV with a supporting statement of no more than 500 words demonstrating why you would be suitable for the role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
